info.description:
Windows Prefetch file parser
******************************
This module is for parsing Windows Prefetch files.

Build Status
============
.. image:: https://img.shields.io/travis/pidydx/winprefetch.svg
        :target: https://travis-ci.org/pidydx/winprefetch

.. image:: https://coveralls.io/repos/yahoo/winprefetch/badge.svg
  :target: https://coveralls.io/r/yahoo/winprefetch

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/dm/winprefetch.svg
    :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/winprefetch/
    
.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/winprefetch.svg
   :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/winprefetch

.. image:: https://pypip.in/py_versions/winprefetch/badge.svg
    :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/winprefetch/

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/l/winprefetch.svg
    :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/winprefetch/

.. image:: https://readthedocs.org/projects/winprefetchbadge/?version=latest
    :target: http://winprefetch.readthedocs.org/en/latest/
    :alt: Documentation Status

Installation
============

To install winprefetch, simply:

.. code-block::

    $ pip install winprefetch

or using easy_install:

.. code-block::

    $ easy_install winprefetch

or from source:

.. code-block::

    $ python setup.py install


Getting Started
===============

.. code-block:: python

    >>> import winprefetch
